import * as React from 'react' import './pageFive.css' import Title from './components/title_bar' import Navbar from './components/nav_bar' import Font from './components/fnt_sze' export default function Membership(){ const [Lang,SetLang]=React.useState('EN') let LangEN,LangDE,grd_LangEN,grd_LangDE; if(Lang === 'EN'){ LangEN = 'block' LangDE = 'none' } else if (Lang === 'DE'){ LangDE='block' LangEN='none' } const [Fntsze,SetFntsze]=React.useState(20) return(
<Navbar onUpdate={(value:string)=>SetLang(value)} pg_Membership='4px solid red'/> <div className='txt_box'> <h1 style={{display:LangEN}}>Membership</h1> <h1 style={{display:LangDE}}>Mitgliedschaft</h1> <Font fntSlct={(sze:number)=>SetFntsze(sze)} LangEN={LangEN} LangDE={LangDE}/> <hr className='hr_a'></hr> <p style={{fontSize:Fntsze}}> At this time, the ICJ constitutes of 156 members. <ol style={{lineHeight:'2em'}}> <li>"Any person interested in the club’s aims can become an ICJ member." (ICJ Statute, 1972).</li> <li>Duly filled application towards membership should be submitted to the ICJ board (E-mail: info@int-club-juelich.de). </li> <li> The annual membership fee, per person and per family is 24€ and 36€ respectively.</li> <li>Each member will be provided with the monthly ICJ program.</li> <li>Members will receive a reduction on the price for excursions.</li> <li>Download the Membership Declaration form</li> </ol> </p> </div> </div> ) }
